original_title: The Church: Goldfish (Jokes, Magic and Souvenirs)
overview: Australian Exclusive! The long-awaited DVD release of The Church's 1990 video collection! a compilation of clips ranging from early touchstones like 'The Unguarded Moment' and 'Electric Lash' through their hit 'Under the Milky Way', 'Metropolis' & 'You're Still Beautiful'. Also includes home video clips and more! 18 total tracks.
title: The Church: Goldfish (Jokes, Magic and Souvenirs)
